KitKat::

She stood near the back of the room.  She saw Quickstrike and smiled. 
Waspinator was there too.  She remembered them and fighting with them 
against the maximals so long ago.  Seeing them stirred old memories 
in her processors.  She smiled at the glorious battles they had 
fought in.  She turned and looked around the room. With so many 
seasoned warriors, surely they would have to win the war.
